<linker>
  <!--
    Talos E2E 运行时程序集在 IL2CPP 构建中必须保留核心反射入口，
    否则 IL2CPP linker 会因缺少直接代码引用而裁剪 E2EAutoInit 及其依赖的类型元数据，
    导致 BDLauncher.TryLaunchTalosE2EInDebugBuild() 通过反射查找类型失败。
    
    Talos E2E runtime assemblies must preserve core reflection entrypoints in IL2CPP builds;
    otherwise the IL2CPP linker strips type metadata for E2EAutoInit and its dependencies
    due to the absence of direct code references, causing BDLauncher.TryLaunchTalosE2EInDebugBuild()
    to fail when looking up the type via reflection.
  -->
  <assembly fullname="Talos.E2E.Runtime" preserve="all"/>
  <!--
    BDFramework.Test 程序集包含宿主侧 E2E 测试用例（LaunchTests、AssetTraversalTests 等），
    这些测试用例仅通过 E2ETestRunner 反射扫描发现，无直接代码引用。
    IL2CPP linker 在无 preserve 声明时会裁剪 E2ETestAttribute 自定义属性元数据，
    导致 GetCustomAttribute<E2ETestAttribute>() 返回 null，测试发现结果为 0。
    
    BDFramework.Test assembly contains host-side E2E test cases (LaunchTests, AssetTraversalTests, etc.)
    that are discovered exclusively via E2ETestRunner reflection scanning with no direct code references.
    Without a preserve declaration, the IL2CPP linker strips E2ETestAttribute custom attribute metadata,
    causing GetCustomAttribute<E2ETestAttribute>() to return null and test discovery to yield 0 results.
  -->
  <assembly fullname="BDFramework.Test" preserve="all"/>
</linker>
